<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 20:08:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙战争粉碎了所有假设，让以色列陷入无计可施的境地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-shattered-all-assumptions-leaving-israel-scrambling-without-a-plan/0000018e-ad3d-d029-a78f-fd3f6c140000</link><description>多年来主导以色列政策的基本信念在 10 月 7 日崩溃了，而且至今仍未被取代，其结果是，以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突有可能蔓延到整个中东 — — 甚至可能超越中东</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 19:07:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-war-shattered-all-assumptions-leaving-israel-scrambling-without-a-plan/0000018e-ad3d-d029-a78f-fd3f6c140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 182 天：中央情报局局长预计将前往开罗进行人质释放谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-182-cia-chief-expected-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-negotiations/0000018e-af1e-d9e9-a9af-effe105a0000</link><description>以色列国防军对杀害援助人员的调查发现，这是由于“一系列可避免的错误”造成的，违反了交战规则。 ■ 联合国人权理事会通过决议，呼吁以色列对可能的战争罪行负责。 ■ 由于担心伊朗，以色列使馆关闭报复 ■ 中央情报局局长预计本周末在开罗会见埃及、以色列和卡塔尔对话者 ■ 战争结束 182 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:44:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-182-cia-chief-expected-in-cairo-for-hostage-release-negotiations/0000018e-af1e-d9e9-a9af-effe105a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称人质可能在 10 月 7 日绑架过程中被以色列国防军直升机误杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-hostage-likely-mistakenly-killed-by-army-helicopter-during-abduction-on-oct-7/0000018e-ae81-d9e9-a9af-eff3a1730000</link><description>以色列国防军的一份声明称，有证据表明，哈马斯恐怖分子用来劫持人质的车辆被空军击中，埃弗拉特·卡茨死亡。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-hostage-likely-mistakenly-killed-by-army-helicopter-during-abduction-on-oct-7/0000018e-ae81-d9e9-a9af-eff3a1730000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡部长在反政府、人质抗议活动中将以色列总检察长称为“人民的敌人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-labels-ag-enemy-of-the-people-amid-anti-govt-hostage-protests/0000018e-aed2-d9e9-a9af-eff2b6130000</link><description>在极右翼部长本格维尔缺席的情况下，安全内阁投票赞成授权内塔尼亚胡和加兰特扩大对加沙的人道主义援助</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 15:39:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-labels-ag-enemy-of-the-people-amid-anti-govt-hostage-protests/0000018e-aed2-d9e9-a9af-eff2b6130000</guid></item><item><title>世界中央厨房的灾难发生在一个已经遭受“以色列疲劳”的世界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/the-world-central-kitchen-debacle-happened-in-a-world-already-suffering-israel-fatigue/0000018e-ae11-dc75-afde-fef1ac430000</link><description>即使在这样的时刻，拜登也明白以色列人也感到害怕。但他似乎并没有完全明白内塔尼亚胡正在利用它们来欺骗他，而且政府不可能将其严厉的语言与照常向以色列出售武器相调和</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 14:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/the-world-central-kitchen-debacle-happened-in-a-world-already-suffering-israel-fatigue/0000018e-ae11-dc75-afde-fef1ac430000</guid></item><item><title>联合国人权理事会要求以色列对“可能的战争罪行”承担责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/un-human-rights-council-demands-israel-be-held-accountable-for-possible-war-crimes/0000018e-ad9c-d029-a78f-fdbe78b10000</link><description>28个国家对该决议投了赞成票，13个国家弃权，6个国家反对，其中包括美国和德国。以色列联合国代表表示“投赞成票就是投给哈马斯”</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 11:55:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/un-human-rights-council-demands-israel-be-held-accountable-for-possible-war-crimes/0000018e-ad9c-d029-a78f-fdbe78b10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡剩下的就是以以色列付出巨大代价来争取更多时间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/all-that-remains-for-netanyahu-is-to-buy-more-time-at-a-great-cost-to-israel/0000018e-ad43-d845-ad9e-edd357a50000</link><description>即使在 10 月 7 日之后，大多数公众似乎迫切希望摆脱他，总理的集团仍然保持稳定，没有任何真正的叛乱迹象。现在，他可以在赫尔佐格和甘茨的沉默中得到安慰</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 11:10:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/all-that-remains-for-netanyahu-is-to-buy-more-time-at-a-great-cost-to-israel/0000018e-ad43-d845-ad9e-edd357a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称“一系列错误”导致加沙世界中央厨房工人被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-series-of-mistakes-led-to-killing-of-world-central-kitchen-workers-in-gaza/0000018e-acb9-d906-a5cf-aebd1f560000</link><description>以色列陆军委员会的调查结果已提交给 WCK 和外国大使，该委员会指出了通信中断、目标错误识别和违反协议的情况。据军方称，这一事件本来是可以避免的</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 10:30:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-series-of-mistakes-led-to-killing-of-world-central-kitchen-workers-in-gaza/0000018e-acb9-d906-a5cf-aebd1f560000</guid></item><item><title>“耶路撒冷有很多无法解释的事情”：游览一座鬼城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jerusalem-has-a-lot-of-unexplainable-things-taking-a-tour-around-a-city-of-ghosts/0000018e-aaa4-dc42-a3de-aab6ad0a0000</link><description>导游 Itamar Farhi 多年来一直在进行“耶路撒冷的恐惧与厌恶”之旅，展示了这座城市所有最残酷的地点。在下个星期五 13 号之前，《国土报》将进行可怕的旅程</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 08:12:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jerusalem-has-a-lot-of-unexplainable-things-taking-a-tour-around-a-city-of-ghosts/0000018e-aaa4-dc42-a3de-aab6ad0a0000</guid></item><item><title>外国外交官表示，以色列与哈马斯的谈判可能持续数周，但协议并不是内塔尼亚胡的首要任务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomat-says-israel-hamas-talks-could-last-weeks-deal-isnt-netanyahus-priority/0000018e-aa9d-d906-a5cf-aa9d03600000</link><description>这位特使表示，他可以看出哈马斯将拒绝最新的停火提议，因为它与之前的提议没有太大不同</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 03:02:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/foreign-diplomat-says-israel-hamas-talks-could-last-weeks-deal-isnt-netanyahus-priority/0000018e-aa9d-d906-a5cf-aa9d03600000</guid></item><item><title>六个月后，以色列-加沙战争的目标几乎没有实现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/after-six-months-few-of-the-israel-gaza-wars-goals-have-been-achieved/0000018e-aa80-d029-a78f-faa25a8a0000</link><description>尽管对加沙发动地面入侵有一定的逻辑性，但必须承认失败：期望太高，与美国的紧张局势加剧，人质仍在加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 03:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/after-six-months-few-of-the-israel-gaza-wars-goals-have-been-achieved/0000018e-aa80-d029-a78f-faa25a8a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列下次选举倒计时已经开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/countdown-to-elections/0000018e-aa6b-ddd5-a7ef-afebc00d0000</link><description>即使本尼·甘茨还没有决定做什么，事情正在滚动，沸腾的街道和以色列两极分化的政治的动态将决定现实：提前选举，很快</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 03:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/countdown-to-elections/0000018e-aa6b-ddd5-a7ef-afebc00d0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们把爸爸带回以色列的家。他可以在这里继续梦想”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-05/ty-article/.highlight/we-brought-dad-home-to-israel-he-can-keep-dreaming-here/0000018e-ac0f-ddd5-a7ef-af8fab060000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对兄妹陪伴他们的父亲踏上返回祖国的最后一程，还有一位年轻的以色列人，她的奶奶拒绝告诉她大屠杀的故事</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 02:49:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-04-05/ty-article/.highlight/we-brought-dad-home-to-israel-he-can-keep-dreaming-here/0000018e-ac0f-ddd5-a7ef-af8fab060000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯实际上相信它会征服以色列。在准备过程中，它将国家分为几个州</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-actually-believed-it-would-conquer-israel-and-divided-it-into-cantons/0000018e-ab4a-dc42-a3de-abfad6fe0000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，数以万计的加沙人逃往埃及，其中许多人是有能力支付巨额费用的精英人士。我在开罗遇到了老朋友，他们仍然对哈马斯领导层的救世主疯狂感到惊讶</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 02:12:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-actually-believed-it-would-conquer-israel-and-divided-it-into-cantons/0000018e-ab4a-dc42-a3de-abfad6fe0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党主席誓言对伊朗将军遇刺事件进行“明确”报复；以色列国防部长：“我们正在准备”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-live/israel-to-take-immediate-steps-to-increase-gaza-aid-via-ashdod-port-erez-crossing/0000018e-abe2-dc75-afde-fbf213160000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，被绑架的以色列人很可能在 10 月 7 日的绑架事件中被军用直升机开火打死 ■ 安全内阁授权扩大对加沙的援助，本格维尔声称在他抵达之前故意举行投票 ■ 美国正在查看有关以色列使用人工智能识别加沙轰炸目标的报告 ■ 世界中央厨房要求对空军工作人员遇害事件进行独立调查</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 01:41:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-live/israel-to-take-immediate-steps-to-increase-gaza-aid-via-ashdod-port-erez-crossing/0000018e-abe2-dc75-afde-fbf213160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院：没有足够的人道主义援助进入加沙地带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-not-enough-humanitarian-aid-is-getting-into-the-gaza-strip/0000018e-aace-d906-a5cf-aadedc8d0000</link><description>在高等法院就人权组织提交的请愿书进行听证时，法官要求州政府解释为什么不允许更多援助进入拉斯维加斯大道</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 00:05:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-not-enough-humanitarian-aid-is-getting-into-the-gaza-strip/0000018e-aace-d906-a5cf-aadedc8d0000</guid></item><item><title>在新加坡航展上，加沙战争是以色列武器制造商的一个卖点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/at-singapore-airshow-the-gaza-war-was-a-selling-point-for-israeli-weapon-manufacturers/0000018e-aa7f-dc75-afde-faff383b0000</link><description>新加坡公布从以色列购买的武器；以色列公司推出下一代巡飞弹药；和反无人机技术制造商回忆起10月7日接到的紧急电话。参观亚洲最大的军火贸易展</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:44:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/at-singapore-airshow-the-gaza-war-was-a-selling-point-for-israeli-weapon-manufacturers/0000018e-aa7f-dc75-afde-faff383b0000</guid></item><item><title>定居点安全负责人加入了对拉马拉附近巴勒斯坦村庄的残酷袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/settlement-security-head-joined-brutal-raid-of-palestinian-village-near-ramallah/0000018e-aa94-dc75-afde-faf40c770000</link><description>Mukhmas 村的目击者称，大约 30 名以色列人进入他们的农田并殴打居民；以色列国防军：事件发生前有报道称以色列牧羊人遭到袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 22:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/settlement-security-head-joined-brutal-raid-of-palestinian-village-near-ramallah/0000018e-aa94-dc75-afde-faf40c770000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯杀害的加拿大人的家人起诉本国政府，要求延长对近东救济工程处的援助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-canadians-killed-by-hamas-sue-own-government-over-renewing-aid-to-unrwa/0000018e-ab12-d906-a5cf-ab96733b0000</link><description>申请者认为，鉴于近东救济工程处与哈马斯的关系，政府的决定是“不合理的”，而哈马斯被加拿大法律定义为恐怖组织</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 21:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-05/ty-article/.premium/families-of-canadians-killed-by-hamas-sue-own-government-over-renewing-aid-to-unrwa/0000018e-ab12-d906-a5cf-ab96733b0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗可以威胁。但只有两个字让以色列人真正感到恐慌：“别担心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-04/ty-article/.highlight/iran-can-threaten-but-only-two-words-make-israelis-really-panic-dont-worry/0000018e-aa3e-ddd5-a7ef-afbe3b820000</link><description>也许如果那些负责我们福祉的人不愿意验证我们的情绪，而是宁愿同时用没有信息和太多信息来压倒我们，我们将不得不亲自验证它们</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 20:23:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-04/ty-article/.highlight/iran-can-threaten-but-only-two-words-make-israelis-really-panic-dont-worry/0000018e-aa3e-ddd5-a7ef-afbe3b820000</guid></item></channel></rss>